### üì¶ **Better Solution: Smush Plugin for Lazy Loading**

The Smush plugin provides superior lazy loading because it:
- ‚úÖ Works with all image types (including WebP)
- ‚úÖ Handles responsive images automatically  
- ‚úÖ Provides fallback for older browsers
- ‚úÖ Integrates with WordPress media library
- ‚úÖ No CSS linting issues

