- ‚úÖ **Database Persistence** - Real PostgreSQL storage
- ‚úÖ **Admin User Creation** - Automatic admin setup in DB
- ‚úÖ **Health Checks** - Built-in monitoring
- ‚úÖ **Security** - Production authentication
- ‚úÖ **Scalability** - Containerized deployment
- ‚úÖ **Auto-migrations** - Database schema updates

